reviewText: It's Zaky's Ramadan. This DVD is exactly what I expected it to be. Basic information, easy for small children to relate to and understand. Jazak'Allah to brothers producing these films for the smallest of our ummah!

I had high hopes for this but the graphics are extremely basic and the words don't match the mouths. The storyline is simply too slow when compared to the dozens of good children's shows that it simply won't attain their interest.
